_sText:
A great arena map with mostly pistols but some smg's in the middle on a ramp
a bunch of ways to play this map, but the best is probably to just run over the ramp shooting a lot, theres one bunker kindof thing on each side with one way in but windows as extra exits in case you're caught camping and need to bail out
grenades are really useful in this map because the other team are always just around the corner or on top of you

if you want to make a map request, add me on steam or shoot me a mail
